{"tid":744852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【網民hot talk】 懶理隧道職員驅趕　暖男司機獅隧救貓B","createTime":"2018-07-16T09:14:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T10:28:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3f819592e8d79a6932962a93898626715da277ed","tid":744852,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T09:14:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180716/20451537\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180716%2F20451537&d=nMFf4G2X1VZq%2Bl%2B5tUcDgTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=e2745401\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180716%2F20451537&h=cd3258cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180716/20451537</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年07月16日 <br />\n<br />\n【網民hot talk】<br />\n懶理隧道職員驅趕　暖男司機獅隧救貓B<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港道路擠塞成為常態，每逢假日各大主要道理更非常擠迫，其中隧道成為重災區，前日有司機在隧道口塞車期間在路邊發現小貓B，更與其他司機合作「封路」，最終成功將小貓救走。<br />\n<br />\n網民將車Cam片段上載到Facebook「小心駕駛(討論別人駕駛態度)」群組，表示在前日（7月14日）下午約1時在獅子山隧道口行駛期間，突然見到一隻小貓在橫過道路險象橫生，期間有車輛見狀收慢，正當小貓走到貨車底後，貨車有意識地煞掣，司機隨即下車尋找小貓下落，而前車司機亦參與其中，雖然驚動職員疏導交通，但他亦成功將小貓救走，更在網上發起改名活動。<br />\n<br />\n「幫手諗下叫咩名，有人提議個名叫；葵扇&mdash;&mdash;小葵原因前車係Spade；譚仔&mdash;&mdash;跟奴才個性；獅子&mdash;&mdash;因?係獅子山隧橋汁(執)番嚟；後福&mdash;&mdash;大難不死」  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片：老鼠幫襯大家樂　閃電被逐<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n今日焦點‧即聽"},{"pid":"6832fcf0a6d1987b77df52404b607bbda72a0f50","tid":744852,"uid":56111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T09:15:47.000Z","msg":"暖男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a2e2667e5a08db1cfb11c6b3cb2e60e2a0a23c4","tid":744852,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T09:22:23.000Z","msg":"隻貓好似腦魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab4b46865b7ee555803a6696cffae03f29e1d821","tid":744852,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T09:24:17.000Z","msg":"汁返去補身牙"},{"pid":"63ed19d161e8025029747fa7f8aaeb0dc7f64ce8","tid":744852,"uid":85591,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ab4b46865b7ee555803a6696cffae03f29e1d821","tid":744852,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T09:24:17.000Z","msg":"汁返去補身牙"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T09:27:24.000Z","msg":"執呀屌你老母<br />\n呀呀屌你老母<br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"c71da67a89211c6662c7d4ee6d9bc141727d46e9","tid":744852,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T09:37:05.000Z","msg":"呢D地方都有貓都ON9，梗係仆街遺棄"},{"pid":"70a35c4126019b857f4b8ff9efdf4ff1923d7cbc","tid":744852,"uid":194630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T09:55:28.000Z","msg":"真男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbcc16d8d5176d5fa35a26d73ef5483b25db1aaa","tid":744852,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T09:57:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支持司機<br />\n不過連登仔鐘意食光環, 支持泰國被困班生番都唔支持隻本地貓"},{"pid":"4d0d0558d36948119d6d3e8fe56fc4cd51e67317","tid":744852,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T10:28:50.000Z","msg":"美國有鴨群過馬路，d 車停低等佢地過"}]}